items.title: Asian stocks rise as traders await fed decision
items.description: Asian stocks climbed ahead of the Federal Reserve's policy decision, with uncertainty around the size of the expected rate cut boosting risk assets. Japanese shares surged as the yen weakened, favoring exporters.
